name: Garage JL Lefrançois
overview:
We offer the best value for new or used farm tractors and equipment for your money

At Garage J.L. Lefrançois, our mission is to offer our customers full size as well as compact new or used tractors or equipment of the highest quality at the best possible price. This is why we put extra care into the inspection cleaning and preparation of the equipment we deliver.

We are specialized in used tractors, new tractors, farm machinery and equipment

At Garage J.L. Lefrançois, we know that your time is precious, and that is why you need equipment that is best in class and will answer your needs. Our professional sales personal are there to listen to you and help you make the right choice for your equipment needs either used or new. We are proud to offer only first quality products.

We are representing some of the best brands, McCormick for farm and compact tractors, Kioti for compact and utility tractors, Gravely for commercial and consumer lawn equipment, Ariens for lawn and snow equipment Stihl and Echo for chain saws and trimmers.
